node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Hot Dudes Reading on July 05, 2021. May be an image of 1 person and beach.

node.text: I’m so excited to celebrate freedom that I’m doing it twice this year, and this red, white and blue vision looks like the perfect post-Independence Day date. His smooth, kissable face is mask-free, and that tanned torso is shirt-free. Now once we find a beach-side bar and toast to our nation’s freedom, we can work on freeing his waist of those shorts. #Happy4thOfJuly #And5th #GetStarSpangledHammered #hotdudesreading

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Hot Dudes Reading on May 19, 2021. May be an image of 1 person and sitting.

node.text: This LA loner looks ripe for a coffee speed date, and lucky for him, I’ve got some questions brewing. How rough does he grind his beans? What’s his ideal number of pumps? Is he more of a heavy cream or froth kind of guy? Here’s to hoping our caffed-up cuddle will lead to something hot and strong. #AndBottomless #HDRarchive #hotdudesreading

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Hot Dudes Reading on May 05, 2021. May be an image of 2 people, people standing, overcoat and indoor.

node.text: Call me Punxsutawney Phil because I’m officially calling for six more weeks of winter. Maybe it's today’s chilly vibes, but I’m just not ready to say goodbye to trench coat Tarzans like this. This guy is long and lean, and I want to be everywhere in between. #JustLikeAHotDog #GimmeThemBuns #HDRarchives #hotdudesreading

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Hot Dudes Reading on March 18, 2021. May be an image of 1 person, sitting and indoor.

node.text: Fingers crossed this textbook-touting treasure is a med student because I'm feeling a bit unstable imagining him in a pair of scrubs. I’ll even let him practice giving me a thorough checkup. First suggestion — put a cuff around me and start pumping. #LetsPutTheXInExam #HDRarchives #hotdudesreading

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Hot Dudes Reading on March 15, 2021. May be an image of 2 people, people standing and indoor.

node.text: This smoke show looks like he just stepped out of a GQ fashion spread and onto the 6 train. He's looking effortlessly cool in all those layers while I’m over here burning up like a whore in church. Here’s to hoping he’ll let go of that pole and grab the nearest hose because I’m on fire. #StopDropAndRollAroundWithMe #HDRarchives #hotdudesreading ⁠

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Hot Dudes Reading on March 12, 2021. May be an image of one or more people, people sitting and indoor.

node.text: This stoic stallion must be a history buff, and I’m ready to learn all about his past. Where's he from? Any siblings? Mom’s maiden name? Once the basics are covered, we can move on to the important questions. When does he want me to move in? Does he want a dog? What will we name it? Will Rex be allowed to sleep on the bed? #StageFiveClinger #ImSoLonely #LetMeMoveIn #HDRarchives #hotdudesreading

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Hot Dudes Reading on March 09, 2021. May be an image of 1 person and book.

node.text: Just when I’d almost given up hope of meeting my soulmate, I see this knockout reading about the creation of the ideal genetic organism. Put the book down and take a seat, gorgeous - your parents already cracked the code. #TalkNerdyToMe #HDRarchives #hotdudesreading

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Hot Dudes Reading on March 05, 2021. May be an image of 2 people, people sitting and indoor.

node.text: San Francisco's electric buses are silent compared to the screeching subways back home, and it looks like this manly Muni-rider is enjoying the break. Once he realizes he's in a reserve seat, he'll have no choice but to sit in the one I'm saving next to me. And he’s about to appreciate that I know exactly when to be quiet.  #AndWhenToGetLoud #HDRarchives #hotdudesreading

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Hot Dudes Reading on March 01, 2021. May be an image of 1 person, sitting and indoor.

node.text: Well hello there, doesn't he look like a sophistica…wait, is that a Jansport? The leather jacket and purple backpack combo is throwing me off, but maybe I could get used to this. Mornings reading Hemingway followed by afternoons drinking like Hemingway. Nights at the museum, followed by later nights on the dance floor. Contradictions haven’t looked this good since Billy Ray Cyrus’ hair.  #AchyBreakyMyBed #HDRarchives #hotdudesreading

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Hot Dudes Reading on February 25, 2021. May be an image of 1 person, beard, sitting and indoor.

node.text: This Milanese man has got me feeling VERY weak in the knees - it must be amorè! Maybe my blood sugar is low, but all of a sudden, I’m craving a hearty noodle dish. Pass the spaghetti  because I'm ready to be his lady AND a tramp. #DontForgetTheMeatballs #HDRarchives #hotdudesreading

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Hot Dudes Reading on February 22, 2021. May be an image of 1 person, sitting and indoor.

node.text: My Monday blues were in full swing till I caught a glimpse of this multitasking man. Music in his ears, coffee in one hand, and a book in the other - I see his talent boding well for our future. While he's working to give me a foot massage with one hand and pouring wine with the other, I'll be free to use mine for a different kind of job.  #JustWarmingUp #ThisAintMiddleSchool #hotdudesreading #HDRarchives⁠

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Hot Dudes Reading on February 18, 2021. May be an image of 1 person, sitting and indoor.

node.text: Get a load of this ten from Toronto. With that sort of laser concentration and power stance, this one must be a hockey player. Wonder if he's more comfortable playing offense or defense? Doesn't matter because I plan on scoring with him not once, not twice, but three times tonight. #HatTricksByAHotTrick  #HDRarchives #hotdudesreading
